147
00:07:19,572 --> 00:07:22,175
No you tell me what's
your big idea here?

148
00:07:22,242 --> 00:07:24,844
You followed me from the
fighting arena, didn't you?

149
00:07:24,844 --> 00:07:26,413
What?

150
00:07:26,413 --> 00:07:28,481
Then you're really the man called...?

151
00:07:29,883 --> 00:07:33,119
