as the Butcher Demon,

152
00:07:33,553 --> 00:07:35,588
the champion of the Purgatory.

153
00:07:50,904 --> 00:07:52,605
Hey, are you okay with this?

154
00:07:52,739 --> 00:07:54,207
Serving us tea and all.

155
00:07:54,441 --> 00:07:56,976
We could be Hellboy here
to slay the demon, right?

156
00:07:57,077 --> 00:07:58,144
Are you okay with this?

157
00:07:58,144 --> 00:08:01,047
