175
00:08:34,114 --> 00:08:37,417
<i>and before I knew it, everyone</i>
<i>called me the Butcher.</i>

176
00:08:38,852 --> 00:08:40,620
<i>I was eventually sent to jail</i>

177
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:43,490
<i>and had nothing to do but</i>
<i>to wait for my head to roll.</i>

178
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:47,160
<i>But someone had their eye on</i>
<i>me and paid to get me out of jail.</i>

179
00:08:47,394 --> 00:08:49,195
